10. Intranet
Definition
A private network accessible only within an organization.
Features
Internal communication
Employee portals
Internal documents
Examples
Company HR Portal
College ERP
11. Extranet
Definition
An extension of an intranet allowing controlled external access.
Users
Vendors
Suppliers
Partners
